name: Sea World San Diego

name: Legoland
description: Legoland California is a theme park, miniature park, and aquarium located in Carlsbad, California, based on the Lego toy brand.

name: UCSD

name: SDSU

name: USD

description: If the photograph of raising the American flag on Iwo Jima is the quintessential World War II icon for triumph in a just war, then 'Unconditional Surrender' is the icon for the just rewards of victory.
